data.description: Nestled in the coveted Paradise West neighborhood of Albuquerque, this exceptional 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans 1,728 square feet and sits gracefully on a generous .23-acre lot with the convenience of room for RV parking. A haven for relaxation and entertainment, this residence features a sparkling pool that beckons on warm New Mexico days, creating an oasis in your backyard. The meticulously landscaped surroundings enhance the allure of this property, providing a perfect balance of privacy and outdoor enjoyment. Inside, the well-appointed 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 2 living areas ensure ample space for family living, making this residence the epitome of a harmonious blend of comfort and style in the vibrant heart of Albuquerque's Paradise West community.
